---
title: Creamy Cherry Tomato, Beef & Chorizo Fusilli with Baby Leaves & Parmesan Cheese
description: Whip up a pasta dinner like no other, filled to the brim with beef, mildly spiced chunks of chorizo, a burst of sweetness from the fresh cherry tomatoes and a rich creamy sauce stirred through to bring it all together. Top it off with a fresh herb and some Parmesan cheese.
